# Never commit private keys
**/private/
**/private/*
*.key
*.key.pem

# Usually generated PKI state/artifacts
**/newcerts/
**/crl/
**/*.crl
**/index.txt
**/index.txt.*
**/serial
**/serial.old
**/crlnumber
**/crlnumber.old

# Usually generated CSRs
**/csr/*.pem
**/csr/*.csr

# Keep cert dirs, but ignore generated cert PEMs by default
**/certs/*.pem

# Editor junk
*.swp
*~
.DS_Store
